<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/32060626.265406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdz=
L2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMTIvc2hvcGlmeS1zaGFtZXMtd29ya2Vycy13aXRoLWEtMS02MDA=
tcHJpY2UtdGFnLWZvci1wb2ludGxlc3MtbWVldGluZ3M_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDcxMjIzX01PTkVZU1=
